" Set colorscheme to a light theme, PaperColor is a popular choice
colorscheme PaperColor

" If PaperColor is not installed, you can set a default light theme like this:
" colorscheme ron

" Enable line numbers
set number

" Highlight current line - optional, but improves visibility
set cursorline

" Move to the match as you type your search
set incsearch

" Enable syntax highlighting
syntax on

